name.text:
Dose 1 PCV 13 at 24 m-4 days.  Series complete. 
Evaluation_Test_Type: All Valid: Forecast Test
General_Description: This test case describes when a child is administered the first  dose of the Pneumococcal 13 vaccine at 24 months - 4 days, that the dose is considered to be valid. No additional doses are recommended.  The series is complete.
